DAF_RegisterImportStatus.da_description: The Register Import Status provides information about the status of the Register Data imports, as to what the most recent imported Register Data package is, and the corresponding most recent Event created as part of this data import package.

lastEventId.da_description: Last Event ID of the imported register data package.

lastSequenceNumber.da_description: Last finished register import data packages sequence number.

lastUpdated.da_description: The date and time for when this current Register Import Status row was last updated.

PageInfo.da_description: Information about pagination in a connection.

hasNextPage.da_description: Indicates whether more edges exist following the set defined by the clients arguments.

hasPreviousPage.da_description: Indicates whether more edges exist prior the set defined by the clients arguments.

startCursor.da_description: When paginating backwards, the cursor to continue.

endCursor.da_description: When paginating forwards, the cursor to continue.
